title: Ubehage's EasyCopy v2.3
description:
Ubehage's EasyCopy v2.3
-----------------------
"Small, Fast and Easy to use!"

Here is an update to this user- and nerd-friendly tool for copying/moving around with files and folders.

Updates in this release:
- Drag'n'Drop is back!
- Added customizable buffering.
